videos.description: Melvin Frazier blows by his defender with a nifty move and gets big air before throwing down the emphatic one-handed slam over another UNC defender.
videos.headline: Tulane's Frazier throws down monster slam

videos.description: Brandon Huffman gets the dish from Theo Pinson and finishes strong for the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: UNC's Huffman rocks the rim

videos.description: Luke Maye protects the basket by swatting away a Cameron Reynolds shot attempt in the first half.
videos.headline: UNC's Maye denies Tulane

videos.description: Mike Couzens and Jason Capel breakdown a 22-point performance from Luke Maye, as the Tar Heels win big 97-30.
videos.headline: UNC too much for Tulane

videos.description: Luke Maye scores 22 points and grabs 10 rebounds in North Carolina's 97-73 win over Tulane.
videos.headline: Maye shines in UNC's blowout win over Tulane
